title: RPG Real Estate
description: The story begins 15 years after the demon king was defeated and the world has become peaceful. Kotone, who graduated from school and became a magician, inquired about the kingdom-affiliated RPG Real Estate in order to find a new home. In reality, RPG Real Estate was Kotone's place of employment, and together with Fa, a demi-human, the priest Rufuria, and the soldier Rakira, they help support the searches of new homes for the customers with various circumstances.

episodes.title: Welcome to RPG Real Estate! Room-Searching for the First Time!
Troublesome Property! First Business Trip to the Dark Lord's Castle
For Real! Dragon, Ghost, Overwhelming Magic!?
Stay Together! A Tightly Packed Room of Pets, Dreams and Friendships!
Summer! I Found a Great House that Suits my Swimsuit!
A Melody for the Grim Reaper!? We're All Friends! Let's Get Along!
Doors, Doors, Doors! Open the Door to Summer Vacation!
Wha!? Finding a Dream Home through Fortune Telling!?
Nyan! One More Deal Until We Meet Our Goal! Let's Make Our Wishes Come True at the Millennium Star Festival!
Woes of Longevity! I Need a Sturdy House That I Can Live in for a Long Time!
Thanks, Everyone! RPG Real Estate's New Journey Begins!
